<div class="banner">
  <div class="banner-content text-center">
    <h1>Discrete, professional advice for your skin problems!</h1>
    <%= link_to "Get advice", questions_path, class: "btn btn-solid"  %>
    <p><i class="fas fa-angle-down"></i></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper-light-grey">
  <div class="stats-container">
    <h2>
      <mark class="green">85% of adolescents</mark> experience at least minor acne
    <hr>
    </h2>
    <p>
      Your skin can change over time for many reasons, such as puberty, nutrition, and genetic predispositions. Instead of feeling embaressed or receiving wrong advice on the internet you can now get help to solve your problem.
      <br>
      <br>
      SkinClean helps you check your skin condition confidentially. Professional doctors will provide you with scientifically sound information and recommend the appropriate medicine and a dermatologist near you.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="wrapper-white">
  <div class="green-header">
    <h1>
      GETTING STARTED
      <hr>
    </h1>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <div class="process-card">
        <div class="process-card-image-container">
          <div class="circle">
        <%= image_tag "chat.svg", class: 'process-card-image'%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card-description">
          <h2>
            Answer basic questions
          </h2>
          <p>
            Talk to our chatbot “Claire” and provide us with some initial information to help us categorize your condition.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <div class="process-card">
        <div class="process-card-image-container">
          <div class="circle">
        <%= image_tag "camera.svg", class: 'process-card-image'%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card-description">
          <h2>
            Upload picture of your condition
          </h2>
          <p>
            Open the SkinClean camera and take a photo of your face. Please ensure sufficient lighting and clarity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <div class="process-card">
        <div class="process-card-image-container">
          <div class="circle">
        <%= image_tag "doctor.svg", class: 'process-card-image'%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card-description">
          <h2>
            Receive diagnosis
          </h2>
          <p>
            SkinClean gives you indicative, free advice from our in-house dermatologists on the next steps to take.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

